text: Apas Jumagulov (; ) (born 19 September 1934) is a Kyrgyzstani politician. He was the Prime Minister of Kyrgyzstan from 14 December 1993 to 24 March 1998. He was the Ambassador to Germany from 1998 to 2003, and to Russia from 2005 to 2007. ==Other websites== *Apas Jumagulov at Radio Free Europe Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Kyrgyzstan Category:Ambassadors to Russia
